Privacy Policy

Protecting the Creativity and Privacy of Our Young Heroes

{/* Header Image */}

Welcome to Canvas of Care

We are dedicated to creating a safe, inspiring space for children aged{" "} 5 to 15 battling cancer. Their creativity, imagination, and privacy are our top priorities.

What Information We Collect

We collect only the minimum necessary information to keep our platform safe and fun. This may include:

  • First name or nickname
  • Age range (not exact birthdate)
  • Art submissions, creative works, and messages shared on the platform
  • Parent/guardian contact information (for consent)

How We Use This Information

We use the information to:

  • Display creative works on the platform
  • Celebrate children's achievements in art challenges
  • Ensure a safe and positive experience
  • Communicate with parents/guardians if needed

Who Can See This Information?

Only platform moderators and parents/guardians can see detailed information. Creative works may be shared publicly, but personal information is always kept{" "} private.

Your Rights and Choices

Parents/guardians can:

  • Request to review or delete their child's information
  • Withdraw consent at any time

Safety First!

We are fully committed to child safety and follow{" "} COPPA guidelines to ensure all children are protected online.

Contact Us

If you have any questions, please reach out to us at:
Email: support@canvasofcare.com

© 2025 Canvas of Care. All Rights Reserved.
